Dialogue: 2,0:34:40.61,0:34:43.01,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的信息简短但神秘
Dialogue: 2,0:34:43.49,0:34:45.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“感谢你的善意来信
